@@ -0,0 +1,17 @@
+Drop bookmaker logo files here named by key, e.g.:
+  sportsbet.png
+  tab.png
+  betr.png
+  bet365.png
+  ladbrokes.png
+  neds.png
+  pointsbet.png
+  unibet.png
+
+Square images work best (they're shown at ~20px, rounded). PNG or SVG both work —
+if you use SVG, just also add a same-named .png as fallback isn't required,
+the app requests "<key>.png" by default. If you'd rather use .svg, tell Claude
+and it'll switch the extension in BookmakerBadge.
+
+Until a file exists for a key, the app shows a small coloured initials badge
+instead automatically — no broken images.
